data.description: WELCOME to 2687 Dawson Cabin Rd.  This home is almost like new construction.  The roof and HVAC are only a few years old but the owners have done all the other updating you could want.  ALL new electrical panel, and all new lighting throughout.  Brand new septic which goes with the new and updated bathrooms.  New shower/tub surrounds, and toilets.  The kitchen has been updated with all new cabinets, counter tops, and appliances!  Brand new flooring and paint throughout.  SO MUCH NEW but the charm of country living.  All work has been permitted and inspected but the county.
